@startuml US-12
title US-12 Search Games by Name

actor User
boundary "Web UI" as UI
control "GameController" as GC
control "GameService" as GS
database "GameRepository" as GR

User -> UI: Type "Cyber" in search bar
UI -> GC: GET /games?query=Cyber
GC -> GS: searchByTitle("Cyber")
GS -> GR: findByTitleContains("Cyber")
GR --> GS: matching games
GS --> GC: results
GC --> UI: 200 OK + results
UI --> User: Render results
@enduml
